metadata.name: Loony Face: Genesis #1
metadata.description: A party of loony souls invading the Ethereum blockchain with loo-nacy, co-branding, and a million stickers... Loony Face: Genesis is a group of 100 council members in the Loony City, leading the citizens to the ultimate madness. Special Benefits: 50% royalty splits of all digital art auctions from Ouyang Ru + 1 free-claimed NFT from Loony Face: Main Collection + MORE.
